House Bill 4075
Sponsored by Representative WRIGHT, Senator SMITH DB, Representatives JAVADI, BOICE;
Representatives EDWARDS, EVANS, HELFRICH, LEVY B, MANNIX, MCINTIRE, MUNOZ,
NELSON, NGUYEN D, NOSSE, OSBORNE, PHAM H, RESCHKE, SCHARF, Senator WEBER
